What type of file is this?  Trojan, keylogger, virus, etc?  Not going to bother downloading to find out, but curious to know.

no trojans or anything. but if u know how tpb runs, you know they dont like links to other sites. this is exactly what this file is. the url is another site--forum where you can download the map files.
I stand corrected on this one.  Typically when someone posts a file such as this it contains some type of malware, or a link to download it.
